name: 円香
text: あ、慰めとかは結構ですので
trans: Just so you know, but there's no need to comfort me.

name: 円香
text:
それとも謝罪が必要でしたか？
この度は至らない結果で申し訳ありません
trans:
Or were you expecting an apology?
Then please allow me to offer my heartfelt regrets for being unable to perform to your expectations today.

name: 円香
text:
これからは心を入れ替えて頑張ります
明日からまたよろしくお願い申し上げます
trans: I look forward to working with you once again from tomorrow, with renewed resolve and vigour.

name: プロデューサー
text:
はは……まあ、落ち込んでないならよかったよ
じゃ、一緒に帰ろうか！　美味いメシ屋でも探しながら……
trans:
Haha... well, glad to see you don't seem too down about it.
Let's go and find ourselves a nice place to eat on the way back!
